            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I could only get this to trigger with my full config, but interestingly, the extui cmd window (non-pager) sometimes does not disappear when pressing a key. I was able to move my cursor down into the `msgsep`:\n\n<img width=\"465\" height=\"126\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3046b25c-4976-4fea-8b4f-0bfd7dc83de4\" />\n\nThis was triggered by simply running `:lua vim.pack.update()` and moving the cursor down with `j`.\n\nIt's possible this is an unrelated bug with ui2 (it doesn't open the pager), but I assume it's related.",
